# ExamLink UI

- Follow ExamLink design tokens: navy `#1A2B5E`, gold `#F0A500`, surface `#F1F4FB`.
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes — never inline `style={{}}` in production code.
- Use Lucide React icons exclusively.
- Reuse shared components from `src/components/ui/`: Badge, Button, Input, Modal, Avatar, SectionHead.
- Brand name is **ExamLink CBT**.
- Use Inter font via `next/font/google`.
- Every list/table needs loading skeleton, empty state, and error state (when wired to API).
- Status badges must match prototype color mapping via `Badge` component.
- Modals for all create/edit/import flows.
